<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.8">
<l>paṭṭaravē rakalalkul pavaḷac cevvāy paṇaineṭuntōḷ piṇaineṭuṅkaṇ pālā miṉcol</l>
<l>maṭṭaviḻuṅ kuḻalikkā vāṉōr kāviṉ maraṅkoṇarntā ṉaṭiyaṇaivīraṇilkaḷ tāva</l>
<l>neṭṭilaiya karuṅkamukiṉ ceṅkāy vīḻa nīḷpalaviṉ tāḻciṉaiyil neruṅku pīṉat</l>
<l>teṭṭapaḻañ citaintumatuc coriyuṅ kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would clasp the feet of him who brought the tree</l>
<l rend="indent">of the celestial’s garden for her in whose loosened curls nectar drips,</l>
<l>With a broad pubis, like a cobra, in silk, coral red lips, long bamboo arms,</l>
<l rend="indent">long doe[-like] eyes, and sweet words like milk,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in Kāḻi where fat, reachable fruit,</l>
<l rend="indent">thick in the low-hanging branches of tall jack trees,</l>
<l>Drip juice, tearing [open] when the red fruit of the dark,</l>
<l rend="indent">long leaved areca tree fall as squirrels leap.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
